{"title":"CF1175B-Catch Overflow","uid":"1546dd1809f28cdefc1c0a246e183f01","slug":"CF1175B","date":"2021-08-10T05:18:36.000Z","updated":"2021-08-11T08:29:04.490Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/CF1175B.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p>用到栈的模拟题~</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<h3 id=\"题意概括\"><a href=\"#题意概括\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题意概括\"></a>题意概括</h3><p>有初始值a=0，进行x次操作，共有如下三种操作模式：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>add：使a增加1</li>\n<li>for num：将其和与之适配的end之间所有操作循环执行num次</li>\n<li>end：与for适配</li>\n</ul>\n<p>如果a的值大于$2^{32}$，输出**OVERFLOW!!!**，否则输出a。</p>\n<h3 id=\"题目分析\"><a href=\"#题目分析\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题目分析\"></a>题目分析</h3><p>没啥好说的模拟-.-</p>\n<p>坑点：for循环经过多次堆叠后每次add操作的值有可能大于longlong范围，当然也有可能多次堆叠后不进行add操作，使得堆叠的值又慢慢变小，因此我们可以利用栈存储堆叠到当前状态下需要循环的总次数，而非单次循环的次数。</p>\n<h3 id=\"代码\"><a href=\"#代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码\"></a>代码</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\">#include &lt;bits&#x2F;stdc++.h&gt;\n#define int long long\nusing namespace std;\nint n, now;\nstack&lt;int&gt; st;\n\nsigned main() &#123;\n\tios::sync_with_stdio(false);\n\tint loop &#x3D; pow(2, 32);\n\tcin &gt;&gt; n;\n\tst.push(1);\n\twhile (n--) &#123;\n\t\tstring command;\n\t\tcin &gt;&gt; command;\n\t\tif (command &#x3D;&#x3D; &quot;add&quot;) &#123;\n\t\t\tnow +&#x3D; st.top();\n\t\t\tif (now &gt;&#x3D; loop) &#123;\n\t\t\t\tputs(&quot;OVERFLOW!!!&quot;);\n\t\t\t\treturn 0;\n\t\t\t&#125;\n\t\t&#125; else if (command &#x3D;&#x3D; &quot;for&quot;) &#123;\n\t\t\tint temp;\n\t\t\tcin &gt;&gt; temp;\n\t\t\tif (temp &#x3D;&#x3D; 0)\n\t\t\t\tcontinue;\n\t\t\tst.push(min(st.top()*temp, loop));\n\t\t&#125; else &#123;\n\t\t\tif (st.empty())\n\t\t\t\tcontinue;\n\t\t\tint temp &#x3D; st.top();\n\t\t\tst.pop();\n\t\t&#125;\n\t&#125;\n\tcout &lt;&lt; now &lt;&lt; endl;\n\treturn 0;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n","text":"用到栈的模拟题~ 题意概括有初始值a=0，进行x次操作，共有如下三种操作模式： add：使a增加1 for num：将其和与之适配的end之间所有操作循环执行num次 end：与for适配 如果a的值大于$2^{32}$，输出**OVERFLOW!!!**，否则输出a。 题目分析...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.1k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"题解","slug":"题解","count":32,"path":"api/categories/题解.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"CodeForces","slug":"CodeForces","count":12,"path":"api/tags/CodeForces.json"},{"name":"恢复OI实力","slug":"恢复OI实力","count":23,"path":"api/tags/恢复OI实力.json"},{"name":"模拟","slug":"模拟","count":5,"path":"api/tags/模拟.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%A2%98%E6%84%8F%E6%A6%82%E6%8B%AC\"><span class=\"toc-text\">题意概括</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%A2%98%E7%9B%AE%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90\"><span class=\"toc-text\">题目分析</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81\"><span class=\"toc-text\">代码</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Aurora","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/svg/Bilibili.svg","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/91730547"},"zhihu":{"icon":"/svg/Zhihu.svg","link":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/ying-zong-pai-wu-seng"}}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"HDU2197-本源串","uid":"db16d1c3f4775338fc6ee6b9aaac01fc","slug":"HDU2197","date":"2021-08-11T06:18:24.000Z","updated":"2021-08-15T07:40:39.521Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/HDU2197.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"简单的递归处理，或者说是思维题？ 题意概括由0和1组成的串中，不能表示为由几个相同的较小的串连接成的串，称为本原串，有多少个长为n（n&lt;=100000000)的本原串？答案mod2008。例如，100100不是本原串，因为他是由两个100组成，而1101是本原串。 题目分析...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.3k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"题解","slug":"题解","count":32,"path":"api/categories/题解.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"恢复OI实力","slug":"恢复OI实力","count":23,"path":"api/tags/恢复OI实力.json"},{"name":"